('htl_wrBll6a5Xa25HG3w', 'hotel', 'the-stanford-inn-by-the-sea-eco-resort', 'en', 'The Stanford Inn by the Sea Eco-Resort', 'Stanford Inn by the Sea sits atop a meadow overlooking organic gardens and Mendocino Bay.  The eco-resort is dedicated to ensuring that its guests are not only pampered, but enriched and enlivened. \n\nEvery detail is attended to, from wood-burning fireplaces set and ready to light, to a salt-water indoor pool, to a sumptuous, varied organic breakfast menu. Inspired by the resort''s Certified Organic farm, the nationally acclaimed Ravens restaurant provides cutting edge vegan cuisine. Guests also enjoy the Inn''s Mendocino Center for Living Well which offers Massage in the Forest, and classes in nutrition, cooking, creative play shops, gardening, Chinese Medicine, nature walks, mushroom foraging, yoga and more. Canoeing, kayaking  and mountain biking are available at the Stanford’s Catch A Canoe and Bicycles Too, providing access to the trails and waterways of the verdant and breathtaking Big River watershed.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/hwZXQ3pqTRl9vyS0.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/bAwRXtXbjkAaCDVB.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/7H9mcGFjTXRNaDO7.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/ZK5EhBPRHCFLKW4J.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/by3Mop5Azb3BdaNJ.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/Ew9TrX82hyWVVFEE.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/H4WVFmFHw0zTc36x.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/V0WGWzsdQRNYKkaN.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/fw5MmFFqy0JhowH5.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/bpTMJXPQ9Fo7zDr6.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/xt446yYdzcQ03pcP.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/PQOVJFplqc4DBTOB.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/4YYZLSGJawCylARS.jpg}', '{healthy,organic,lodge,bythesea,sea,gardens,fireplace,saltwaterpool,pool,indoorpool,gardening,farm,vegancuisine,bicycles,kayaking,yoga,california,usa}', '{"twitter": "https://twitter.com/EcoResort_CA", "website": "ht