('htl_dOCpmRWw8XRNpV9X', 'hotel', 'cal-reiet-holistic-retreat', 'en', 'Cal Reiet Holistic Retreat', ' Cal Reiet is a hCal Reiet Holistic Retreat offers a holistic lifestyle retreat focused on health and wellbeing. It is situated within walking distance from the picturesque village of Santanyi, and only 3.5 km from Cala Santanyi and Cala Llombards Beach. The famous Es Trenc beach is only 20 minutes drive from the hotel.\nThe hotel features an outdoor swimming pool and beautiful gardens. The hotel serves a buffet breakfast in the dining area around the pool. Freshly squeezed fruit and vegetables juices and smoothies can be enjoyed in the pool bar. The restaurant serves only vegetarian with many vegan options cuisine with fresh, locally sourced organic products.\nThe rooms are spacious and tastefully decorated. The suites offer a private kitchen/lounge and terrace to relax in after a busy day. All rooms are equipped with a private bathroom fitted with a shower. For your comfort, you will find bath robes, free toiletries and a hair dryer. \nCal Reiet Holistic Retreat features free WiFi throughout the property.\nYoga classes and massages are offered at the retreat, and an array of other activities is offered in the area, such as cycling, trekking, golfing, horse riding and snorkeling.\nAs the property promotes healthy living, it is not allowed to smoke in the premises or the rooms.\nFree private parking is available on site. The hotel can assist in both bicycle and car hire. The nearest airport is Son Sant Joan Airport, 41 km from Cal Reiet Holistic Retreat. olistic retreat offering its guests a unique holiday experience.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/CwwaetXlBYkXkLQX.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/DQGgpHYd5xHB4TcK.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/2j25AyGGhxQEYJry.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/367BbBMLZ7ZZl2OL.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/PoolqQhmvsbyglv0.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/xqCgcBnhXBjWTZJ6.jpg,https://img-sta