('pst_ZZRQaBTNfXM9SRld', 'post', 'millennials-worry-about-the-environment-should-your-company', 'en', 'Millennials Worry About the Environment -- Should Your Company?', 'Gallup finds that millennials'' concerns about global warming is at a high point\nA climate-focused corporate social responsibility may be meaningful to younger generations\nIf a company''s effort is false or half-hearted, it may drive people away', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/KboZj4oKqBQZlcKH.png}', '{environment,workplace,hr,sustainability,millennials,climatechange,corporateresponsability}', '{"link": "https://www.gallup.com/workplace/257786/millennials-worry-environment-company.aspx?utm_source=google&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=syndication"}', '{}', 'approved', 'usr_AGsNFyCDfjshffNJ', 'usr_AGsNFyCDfjshffNJ', 'creator', '2019-07-09 10:56:06.132551+00', 'https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/KboZj4oKqBQZlcKH.png'),
('pfd_acKtRkF9avvS3SVJ', 'packagedfood', 'avocado-toast', '', 'Avocado Toast', 'Avocado toast is a type of open sandwich or toast made with mashed avocado and salt, pepper, and citrus juice on toast. Potential additional ingredients that enhance the flavor are olive oil, hummus, red pepper flakes, feta, dukkah, tomato, and many other toppings.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/LaJ5klJYBBW8NbkJ.jpg}', '{avocado,toast}', '{}', '{"country": "AX"}', 'approved', 'usr_YwKR0aJdPa2AVtrb', 'usr_YwKR0aJdPa2AVtrb', 'creator', '2019-07-06 13:58:20.45886+00', 'https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/LaJ5klJYBBW8NbkJ.jpg'),
('pfd_9LVbRf2xqzkqY4Nz', 'packagedfood', 'callowfit-sugar-free-tomato-ketchup-sauce', '', 'Callowfit - Sugar Free Tomato Ketchup Sauce ', 'Sauces and dressings without fat and sugar, with almost 0 calories and a lot of flavor are not? But! Now there are CALLOWFIT ® sauces and dressings. Stop with water on the plate or soup in the salad! Creamy firm consistency, suitable for salad, meat, fish or just for dipping. Only 1-5 calories per serving make every meal a pleasure to work out.\n\nNo one has to go without taste – whether spicy Italian, smoky grilled, parmesan or a light dill and cucumber note – CALLOWFIT ® sauces complement each meal with a unique, deliciously light taste experience . This is the new CALLOWFIT ® innovation in the taste!', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/OqcoJjQwJdTXNLoz.jpg}', '{sugar,free,ketchup,sauce,tomato}', '{}', '{"country": "TO"}', 'approved', 'usr_YwKR0aJdPa2AVtrb', 'usr_YwKR0aJdPa2AVtrb', 'creator', '2019-07-06 14:05:06.138746+00', 'https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/OqcoJjQwJdTXNLoz.jpg'),
