('pfd_PsxYBVhYOSX6VpNE', 'packagedfood', 'clearspring-organic-avocado-oil', 'en', 'Clearspring - Organic Avocado Oil', 'Cold-pressed from the creamy flesh of Chilean avocados, Clearspring Organic Avocado Oil has a delicious, nutty flavour which is perfect for a large range of dishes. It can be use for dipping with bread, adding colour, smoothness and flavour to dressings, stir-frying and even deep-frying as it has a very high smoke point. It is also cholesterol free, rich in vitamin E, omega 3 and 6 and it’s high in monounsaturated fat. In many countries is it is a recommended ingredient as part of a healthy heart diet.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/b4hGHRpN4DKh3wYS.jpg}', '{}', '{}', '{"labels": ["gluten-free", "nut-free", "organic", "soy-free", "wheat-free"], "country": "GK", "quantity": {"unit": "ml", "quantity": 250}, "allergens": [], "nutrition": [{"name": "protein", "quantity": 0}, {"name": "total-carbohydrate", "quantity": 0}, {"name": "sugars", "quantity": 0}, {"name": "total-fat", "quantity": 92}, {"name": "saturated-far", "quantity": 13}, {"name": "dietary-fibre", "quantity": 0}, {"name": "sodium", "quantity": 0}], "ingredients": [{"name": "avocados", "organic": true}], "calories_per_100g": 828}', 'approved', 'usr_AGsNFyCDfjshffNJ', 'usr_AGsNFyCDfjshffNJ', 'creator', '2019-07-02 21:40:47.982768+00', 'https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/b4hGHRpN4DKh3wYS.jpg'),
('pfd_SPEj5gj9dAR0hhAe', 'packagedfood', 'clarana-leckerlade-chocolate-nougat-spread', '', 'Clarana - Leckerlade Chocolate Nougat Spread ', 'This fantastically smooth and creamy chocolate spread has a wonderful full-bodied taste of aromatic hazelnuts and fine cocoa. It is gluten-free and, like all Clarana products, is free of palm oil. A truly indulgent way to start to the day.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/G6ya9soOX92bYHjE.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/xz0NKx5rAYyTE9Lx.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/sAO2AS8jNjhEAjAP.jpg}', '{leckerlade,vegan,chocolate,smooth,tasty}', '{}', '{"country": "UM"}', 'approved', 'usr_YwKR0aJdPa2AVtrb', 'usr_YwKR0aJdPa2AVtrb', 'creator', '2019-07-08 09:18:46.618906+00', 'https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/G6ya9soOX92bYHjE.jpg'),
('htl_EEOBepsfpJKH0EPW', 'hotel', 'the-vegan-lodge', 'en', 'The Vegan Lodge', 'The Vegan Lodge; located in the Olympos region of Antalya, where nature and history become one. Our aim is to provide an amazing holiday getaway which is also as respectful towards the stunning local environment as possible.  We proudly invite you to enjoy this special holiday concept which is completely vegan based.\nThe Vegan Lodge has a total of 34 rooms all set within 30 acres of beautiful land.  The hotel is built in a unique style with both single and double storey wooden dwellings which are intertwined with nature.  Unlike other concrete style hotels, our hotel has been designed with the architectural understanding required and also materials needed to honour the magnificent nature of the region.\nThe main goal of our concept is to reduce the carbon footprint to the lowest level possible, whilst also providing a second to none holiday atmosphere without harm to the environment but at the same time not needing to sacrifice any of the usual comfort and enjoyment that you require from your getaway.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/gO2SzcnvCY0MGZPD.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/QNPaXjn3xncKRANV.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/sWeVE3mSdnrsJV0R.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/RYNEdSF20D2E7ngX.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/WK5ZAKK5x8ZC0WPH.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/JEy3lAnjrqW0PZ09.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/p8Mv3qYfNRaBqVaD.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/TEPXnP3yS6cT79zs.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/QmEdLXpr8Mj2wJRm.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/4VXOvpvpkMLDrE6J.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/eYfzq2GtvAhv6esA.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/mFNS8jPDOEJ8X4SV.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/HG57aJXpAD9AlHf2.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/SktP3FDxRbLgkxcR.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/9on40bmsxskQXN4h.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/R4snF0J6byX8dzH0.jpg,htt