('htl_lmKv8EkBEWMKAZNV', 'hotel', 'vegan-hotel-la-vimea', 'en', 'Vegan Hotel LA VIMEA', 'Simple is beautiful. South Tyrollean hospitality combined with green principles create the fundament of Italy’s first vegan hotel. The LA VIMEA Biotique Hotel is an honest island of peace where everything is shaped according the Biotique label which was created in 2015. Our signature for an experience where everything is vegan, organic, sustainable, regional & seasonal and handmade.\nSituated in Naturno in South Tyrol, 700 m from Unterstell, Hotel La Vimea boasts a pond and sauna. The hotel has a restaurant that serves only vegan dishes.\nAll rooms come with wooden furnishings and a balcony with views of the mountains. The private bathroom is equipped with a hairdryer, bathrobe and free toiletries.\nGuests can enjoy various activities in the surroundings, including cycling and hiking. Merano is a 20-minute drive from Hotel La Vimea, while Bolzano is 44 km away. ', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/A5mCwnjl46Q5wgka.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/vW9EAbAWFAnExLVc.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/kgcMLaKm7MQy5BLR.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/9TEOm8YGGFNYTzwQ.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/ZyhQhkLrpT5bzjHB.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/PogSomRoGHtAzONF.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/xls6GHdZS3cfMVcP.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/jzJswgnd3hof6f80.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/3a7PH6YtF68GJ4yr.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/zX6Pf2rhz7vYQTMX.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/KgyfYVyaOWl9Ectj.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/SCF62QmNX6eejmBf.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/5TVZ5N0ybPWbN4fn.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/QnyTh2hJzH7GBMy7.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/JyzxCnaMOANSdCfh.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/2SWlkKZpGbHtZffH.jpg}', '{vegan,hotel,veganhotel,tyrol,green,pool,organic,regional,"restaurant ",sauna,woodenfurnishing,mountains,hiking,merano,bolzano,lavim