('rst_j9m05kjdLlE097gL', 'restaurant', 'fed-by-water', 'en', 'fed by water', 'We want everyone to try a cruelty-free, plant-based Mediterranean diet that encourages healthy living and tastes amazing!\nWe believe that it is time for a revolution in food culture; our focus needs to be on the health implications and environmental impact of what we put into our bodies.  \nOur seasonal menus make the most of fresh fruit and vegetables at their seasonal best. Seasonal food tastes better, it’s better value and it’s a better deal for the planet. Wherever we can, we source our ingredients locally; ensuring that our carbon footprint is kept low as possible whilst supporting local businesses. However, we are also committed to offering the most authentic Italian food so some of our ingredients are shipped from Italy –  the only place in where they are produced.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/J7HY9CtNmoocgzTT.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/3e58LJZKsC5wvJbQ.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/mWdYQdmsCglnyp3a.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/yhkgqRHNDKtNTQvL.png,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/E6trvxjHkyKV4La2.png,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/X8oGMsPc2egxp9gp.png,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/02kvWDccy5PPms5C.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/nwVLV2V3xSYMnWJZ.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/LSHGW4ErohYNm7bX.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/J3q5Fyh4Pam6qmck.jpg}', '{vegan,"italian ","sensorial ","pure ","music ","London ","healthy ","foodie "}', '{"twitter": "https://twitter.com/FEDbywater", "website": "http://www.fedbywater.co.uk/", "facebook": "https://web.facebook.com/FED.LONDON", "instagram": "https://www.instagram.com/fedbywater/"}', '{"address": {"city": "London", "country": "GB", "postcode": "E8 2JS", "street_address": "59 Kingsland High St"}, "location": {"latitude": 51.5482805, "longitude": -0.07569360000002234}, "contact_email": "hello@fedbywater.co.uk", "contact_phone": "+44 7490 637200", "opening_hours": [{"seaso