('htl_GWhoVYYQX3QMD2vY', 'hotel', 'hotel-otto-berlin', 'en', 'Hotel OTTO Berlin', 'Environmental sustainability is just as important at the Hotel OTTO as good taste. Therefore each morning we serve an extraordinary breakfast at the breakfast lounge "Etage07” with an exceptional view over the rooftops of Berlin. From 7 a.m. to 12 p.m. you may enjoy our buffet with regional food, fair traded products and weekly changing specialities, including many vegetarian and vegan options.  The "Etage07" is the perfect place to take a little break from the city-jungle in the afternoon. The beautiful rooftop terrace loads for staying in. Free coffee, tea, mineral water, juices and home-made cakes are available between 2 p.m. and 9 p.m.\n\nSurrounded by restaurants, bars, boutiques, theatres, only a short stroll from the famous Kurfüstendamm and the KaDeWe, the Hotel OTTO is the perfect starting point to explore Germany’s pulsating capital. For short trips as well as for business. ', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/q424A5RqsEeFwyaV.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/HYwkshHhH2QMTMv9.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/fyCjRfDpjLM5zsHM.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/MXQFKxJMvJxF7VRq.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/sf4ZLXDEqxDvmYHD.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/pzEHCcFxOJ94zr4c.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/mnFzn3k9w7WWsCSE.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/NT4wD9kKdt7AJslS.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/TpnYf2fazEoPBFWV.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/ZyzTfkenbEdj7hhC.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/m3RowhC4XAjszzpZ.jpg}', '{veganfriendly,veganoption,breakfast,rooftop,roofterrace,berlin,fairtraded,sustainable,charlottenburg,fairtradeproducts,bioproducts,homemade}', '{"website": "http://www.hotelotto.com/", "facebook": "https://web.facebook.com/HotelOTTOBerlin/", "instagram": "https://www.instagram.com/hotelottoberlin/"}', '{"address": {"city": "Berlin", "country": "DE", "postcode": "10623", "street_address": "Kn