('rst_3QbwERnyHzYQy3e2', 'restaurant', 'wypas-restaurant', 'en', 'WYPAS', 'WYPAS is a place where you''ll find that you can go around the world with a vegetable kitchen and come back with a smile, and above all with a full belly;)\nEvery day from 10 to 12 we serve nutritious, warm breakfasts, and from 12:00 we serve a lunch menu. From Wednesday until Saturday, we are open longer (because until 22:00). Then you can also have supper with us, sit with a craft beer or wine from organic crops from sunny Spain.\nThursdays in WYPAS are marked by already famous Kenyan donuts with cardamom, which you can easily order with delivery to your home.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/c58fdHB4so7ORhSO.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/FKdQeVWrRH9TcOf9.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/6crelTXd2OYPM7RD.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/5YBKopRHRlaY7b30.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/CgYnzCyMrgcz9a3Z.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/aT5kBCKfwxDpza0v.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/FpXSwtcqoCGBfm3F.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/RlsLv0NJkQLYXBkP.png,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/0Gdj6FzmkzXbN70m.png,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/OjMKWz6Rcl859Pmw.png,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/5RPkQda5TXjYRfys.png,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/857wRMqglGxoGsZG.png}', '{vegan,"Poznan ","Worldfood ","fusion ","delivery "}', '{"website": "https://wypas.business.site/", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/pg/wypas/", "instagram": "https://www.instagram.com/wypas_vegan/?hl=en"}', '{"address": {"city": "Poznań", "country": "PL", "postcode": "60-512", "street_address": "Jackowskiego 38/1"}, "location": {"latitude": 52.40991469999999, "longitude": 16.897031200000015}, "contact_phone": "+48 61 226 46 00", "opening_hours": [{"season": "Whole year", "periods": [{"open": {"day": 0, "time": "1000"}, "close": {"day": 0, "time": "1800"}}, {"open": {"day": 1, "time": "1000"}, "close": {"day": 1, "time": "1800"}}, {"open": {"day": 2, "time": "1000"},