('pst_5qm8fyvDO8gTAv27', 'post', 'beyond-meat-is-a-disruptor-as-plant-based-meat-industry-sales-poised-to-reach-100-billion', 'en', 'Beyond Meat is a ‘disruptor’ as plant-based meat industry sales poised to reach $100 billion ', 'Jefferies analysts think there’s a good chance McDonald’s will add a plant-based option after Burger King’s Impossible Whopper. \nPlant-based meat is going to be huge in the near future and Beyond Meat Inc. “is a true disruptor and innovator” in the industry, according to JPMorgan analysts.\nShares of Beyond Meat BYND, +7.74%   jumped 8% on Tuesday after the company was initiated at overweight with a $97 price target at JPMorgan. Analysts there say Beyond Meat’s “growth opportunity is extraordinary.” ', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/9dm80PNFOYjcCeyX.jpg}', '{meatalternative,vegan,plantbased,beyondmeat,food,foodindustry,market,mcdonalds,jpmorgan,stock,ipo}', '{"link": "https://www.marketwatch.com/story/beyond-meat-is-a-disruptor-as-plant-based-meat-industry-sales-poised-to-reach-100-billion-2019-05-28"}', '{}', 'approved', 'usr_AGsNFyCDfjshffNJ', 'usr_AGsNFyCDfjshffNJ', 'creator', '2019-07-09 10:56:04.18883+00', 'https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/9dm80PNFOYjcCeyX.jpg'),
