('htl_TTnrOfBnATjkEpk8', 'hotel', 'agrivilla-and-restaurant-i-pini-in-san-gimignano-vegan-and-organic', 'en', 'Agrivilla and Restaurant i pini in San Gimignano - vegan & organic', 'Tuscany. Lush, rolling hills, sunny days, medieval towns, cities filled with history and culture, small roads winding their ways through endless greenery passing countless pine and fig trees. Right amidst the glistening olive groves and the majestic vineyards, not too far from the historic centre of San Gimignano, you can find our vegan Agrivilla i pini, a small, picturesque organic winery. An historic estate. A place to enjoy and relax.\nFind tranquility and privacy. Whether in the salt water pool featuring breathtaking panoramic views, beneath a hundred year old olive tree or in a cozy hammock swinging in the shade of the pine trees. i pini draws an alternative program to a hotel stay: It is where nature meets culture, design tradition and harmony hedonism.\nOur Villa has undergone a natural restoration during the past winter months and now shines in a new ecological design. Alongside our philosophy we choose high quality natural materials such as chalk, hemp, clay, natural terracotta floors and antique wooden furniture. Including everything needed for your vacation in Tuscany such as harmony, comfort, elegance and history.\nYou can also experience history in the centre of San Gimignano which only lies 1,5km away. Including its 14 towers, San Gimignano belongs to one of the best-preserved medieval cities and is part of the UNESCO World Heritage since 1990. The location of the so called ‘medieval Manhattan’ is very strategic. Right in the centre of Tuscany. Between Florence and Siena. Making it the ideal place for a cultural journey on long sunny days.\nDays at the Biotique Agrivilla i pini start with an honest, homemade breakfast in the morning, and in the evening we prepare a carefully chosen classy dinner. Whether you enjoy your eating experience on our panoramic patio including the view on San Gimignano or in our elegant dining area, that is up to you. All meals are 100% vegan and creative. Always using organic ingredients which we prefer to produce ourselves, farm to table.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/KRfAsLBRbEYd5fwF.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/TRht3V5QJXgr2WeD.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/ZwYAKaMVjXhsMHqo.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/2yoh6EYonHXyJQCk.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/pFLL3Eso8Bkz5mQe.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/yHxToEk3ff5Q0Hzf.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/WCxLkdlM2fezwSJ3.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/02dWP2qcGPPs9wx8.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/wED5kgxQ73pzJESx.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/WYZ2tC5qACBqeQgb.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/e0tfWoCVTsWLRF3G.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/tYwh5Mm7sbvxWCZe.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/3akjNEffqlxtmyTD.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/ErkEwncwHm0XJw9H.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/sZcvx0lj5gcMBEeX.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/Mt0tgtEF4Jdq8JXK.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/y5rMPqK2b9HM6AJc.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/TAtT5gPoE6opH3zf.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/SKgwzNYdovlNa8L4.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/3rovtKd49Eya0fod.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/oWWAtp248NZPkXdW.jpg}', '{vegan,tuscany,italy,bio,organic,sangimignano,cookingclasses,wine,pool,homemade}', '{"website": "https://www.ipinitoscana.com/", "facebook": "https://web.facebook.com/AgriturismoIPini?_rdc=1&_rdr", "instagram": "https://www.instagram.com/agrivilla_i_pini/"}', '{"address": {"city": "SI", "country": "IT", "postcode": "53037", "street_address": "Località Santa Margherita"}, "location": {"latitude": 43.467177, "longitude": 11.026174999999967}, "amenities": ["bar", "breakfast", "car-park", "dinner", "event-friendly", "free-wifi", "full-vegan", "group-friendly", "gym", "24hr-reception", "hot-tub", "lunch", "pets-allowe