('htl_XBcwfNWxkmoJgdH0', 'hotel', 'villa-vegana', 'en', 'Villa Vegana', 'One of the first 100% vegan hotels in Europe. Past olive, almond, lemon & orange trees you get to our peaceful and charming little world. Along the way grazing sheep, pigs, donkeys and horses welcome you. Set within a designated conservation area Villa Vegana lies on a 30.000 sqm ground with panoramic views of the Tramuntana Mountains. The mediterranean garden and the pool invite you to relax and let yourself go. Enjoy the relaxing and familiar atmosphere of our little vegan paradise. We serve fresh & creative breakfast-buffet every day and our restaurant offers a wide range of international cuisine. The hotel offers plant based, mostly ecological food, soon from the permaculture-garden. The hotel only uses sustainable and vegan cleaning products and provide you vegan cosmetics not tested on animals for your stay. we don''t have any leather, wool, dawn or silk products. ', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/SNkl3Tfh2bdR9VhC.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/EcHQH4MEa2NDOBEo.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/z7y2AQlLCr4qd37b.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/P72B8QcDdWAXENRP.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/a0BTrPEff7Gbf2oo.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/px3CFNZds0ZqyaWH.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/fODV8OCZjAofV9NL.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/av2RCY9NyqRe66bf.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/N6F62LfqQfdkDPmm.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/Heg0SgOZBgPqnmJB.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/TpX425b0D0ypp9py.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/PjlpSY0eOPTxpraE.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/J5vjoltYd9xXG5we.jpg}', '{vegan,100vegan,100%vegan,fullyvegan,pool,animals,organic,healthy,creativefood,freshfood,mallorca,internationalcuisine,creativecuisine}', '{"website": "http://www.villavegana.com/", "facebook": "https://web.facebook.com/villaveganamallorca/", "instagram": "https://www.instagram.com/villa.vegana/"}', '{"add