('pst_PZBSx4ydDS9APgDt', 'post', 'shorting-beyond-meat-stock-is-beyond-expensive', 'en', '''Shorting Beyond Meat stock is beyond expensive.''', 'Short sellers tried to bet against the shares after they soared in their initial days of trading but now the stock became too expensive to borrow. \nA borrow fee of 68% makes Beyond Meat the most expensive stock to short of all U.S. stocks with over $100 million in short interest.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/O87rrcvrano5RKe7.jpg}', '{beyondmeat,short,stock,investing,business,trade}', '{"link": "https://www.marketwatch.com/story/shorting-beyond-meat-stock-is-beyond-expensive-2019-05-29"}', '{}', 'approved', 'usr_AGsNFyCDfjshffNJ', 'usr_AGsNFyCDfjshffNJ', 'creator', '2019-07-09 10:56:03.541792+00', 'https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/O87rrcvrano5RKe7.jpg'),
