('htl_tFFOObwXJs2O5rWP', 'hotel', 'holzhotel-forsthofalm', 'en', 'Holzhotel Forsthofalm', 'Eco-friendly Holzhotel Forsthofalm offers direct access to ski slopes, hiking and mountain bike trails. Set above Leogang, it features unique wooden architecture, an award-winning restaurant, and the Sky Spa on the rooftop. Internet access is free of charge.\nThe Sky Spa offers 360-degree views, individual relaxation areas, a fireplace lounge, a hammock room, the SPAbar, and a spacious cardio fitness room with floor-to-ceiling windows. An organic herbal sauna, Finnish sauna, salt steam bath, and vitamin bar are also available. The panoramic rooftop bathtub, the sauna, and the steam room can be booked for private use. Massages and beauty treatments based on local herbs and traditions are also offered.\nIt is not only a hotel with affinity to nature and living flair, but also a hotel for the vegan cuisine and an excellent offer of natural wines. Specially chosen local products, prepared on the wood grill, refined with alpine herbs and seasoned from the vegan chef making varied vegan menu options for the guests.\nGuided hikes are offered in summer. A public outdoor pool and a swimming lake are close by. In winter, snowshoe hiking and tobogganing are available.\nThe Holzhotel Forsthofalm was awarded the EU Ecolabel 2012 and the Aphrodite Spa Award for Ecology and Sustainability. ', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/3qHhjovdd34yP4x5.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/LjFPRHSEEtj3zA5C.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/DpgyZhGjLOlCTQ8w.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/06MamhYdx0Z36t6L.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/7E3ZBS0HPNemTE4n.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/pO0A3kj6ZJQoYKHZ.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/0CORr8QkrcJ0TB4T.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/ro7mSv9SkdmRXoBW.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/eLTCVYdWE6jN6Yst.jpg}', '{veganfriendly,ski,skiing,veganoptions,veganmenu,pool,spa,wellness,mountains,alps,views,yoga,fitness