('htl_z2A78CrG5qSA7WTa', 'hotel', 'the-island-hideout-one-level-ahead-co-ltd-di-ai-saelnd-aihde-aath', 'en', 'The Island Hideout (One Level Ahead Co., Ltd.) - ดิ ไอส์แลนด์ ไฮด์เอาท์', 'Thai-style lodges are constructed with eco-friendly building materials from local sources and crowned with natural palm leaf roofs. Designed with organic simplicity in mind, they are crafted to the highest quality and comfort standards in the region, striking the precious balance between open-air living, privacy and tropical luxury.\nSpacious beam-work, three exposed faces with bamboo blinds and an open-air bathroom inspire a strong sense of immersion with your surroundings, complete with breathtaking views of our lush, tree-lined grounds and the sparkling waters of Phang Nga Bay.\nWe deliberately do not offer the typical modern distractions of in-room television or WIFI, affording our treasured guests the unique opportunity to truly surrender to the experience of nature and beauty as intended.\nAt The Hideout, we stand by the belief that the symphony of jungle wildlife, the song of wind in the trees and the whispers of waves against our island shores are the best medicine for your senses!\n\nOur Farm-to-Table Restaurant is vegan-friendly. The main house are located on top of the hill, ensuring stunning views of the south-western peninsula and the Phang Nga Bay. The Hideout features memorable sunrise and sunset views. Dinner is served under the light of candles and stars, the perfect ambience to enjoy our delicious dishes made with fresh natural locally sourced ingredients.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/X80cyhgGqc04bM5k.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/MZtxX7SVMXmcjFx3.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/bBn3DlpoJ3990eyC.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/dRCBeqP4OYP389vM.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/4BevkeyHaa7aEZL0.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/FAmNofOKoxGPHwOh.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/hhzX4GvoDnMoWYCa.jpg,https://img-staging.ve