('htl_fYTmsoZbFcO2aOM9', 'hotel', 'agriturismo-coroncina', 'en', 'Agriturismo Coroncina', 'The property is set in a large private garden, the ideal place to be for who wishes to spent time in the silence of nature, for relaxing in a hammock or rocking in the two-person swing.\nThe bio-pool, located in front of the house, is made of resin without the use of reinforced concrete and has a very low impact on the environment. We use pink Himalayan salt which is a perfect disinfectant.\n\nIn addition to our range of wellness and relaxation, it is a fun experience to cook in the kitchen of the restaurant during one of the various cooking courses that we organize on request throughout the year. You can also visit the organic kitchen garden and, when necessary, pick the vegetables. You can relax or read in the hammock under the porch, walk in the area together with our or your loyal four-legged friend … in short, here at Coroncina it is like home, in complete relaxation.', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/VvqwZmE6WeqEyaTt.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/stGaXLaFBa3D7Ell.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/qYzsmJnp0ykmgFLx.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/xddfR25yzlsdOcvf.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/lercGAzNDraM8VlX.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/BWoR7X0HbqcTPxnY.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/yrh9bjNhhlT3gfKq.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/e8mSTq6GY8Oe3fD5.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/EXykHD7Xb58jDnZo.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/SnngqyvSEFrz0H9L.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/53qn582g8aPTaFEJ.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/fBlqo7kSrJFs0meK.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/5S3fdf96hmhEHSxz.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/WJFWvpQslPNM4YDt.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/MyG7HgCGh2dJ9QxP.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/fyGEjH5p9DKHX5l4.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/2oOKDvDt329YZzah.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/RgvefaN7hqpFHzWe.jpg,https://img