('htl_5KhGEjhlH8z5w8DS', 'hotel', 'the-farm-at-san-benito', 'en', 'The Farm At San Benito', 'The Farm at San Benito is a 5-star resort that offers holistic wellness programs accompanied by exclusive amenities such as a swimming pool, a garden area for wellness activities, and restaurant that specializes in vegan cuisine. Surrounded by greenery, the air-conditioned villas and suites feature a mix of native and modern decor. Some rooms include a balcony, pocket gardens or courtyards and with standalone tubs and private dining areas. All rooms include a flat-screen cable TV, a sofa or daybed, and an en suite bathroom with shower along with his and her sink. Each villa and suite also has a private entrance.\nAlive! restaurant serves gourmet vegan meals prepared in an Asian style. Using fresh, home-grown and organic ingredients, its menu includes vegetable burgers and freshly baked bread.\nAt the resort, guests can opt for specially curated treatments and programs suited for their needs, with the help of the resort''s integrative doctors. Activities such as yoga, Tai Chi, and functional fitness can be arranged for guests. Part of the holistic programs are meditation session, Pilates, and spa treatments. ', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/VgrQZHzzXMmnMMjE.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/djOTxHmMf05kGFBo.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/J7qfQc6AwNPaxPTQ.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/cgXLleFhdjcf0TfD.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/v9SsZJD60tjDZDtB.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/lbqSAa0mOskM5fna.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/WDjGfr9VcDvwRh68.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/OJy5Lo7qrKOMVELQ.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/yhhNSY6x0xRp3WtA.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/NnSkD7JAswsaXhcE.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/OpEbs9B9hf23xSC6.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/cdDrlQAVy9XgzTxT.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/7pf2wpdnm7jLTBnh.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/DpzYe74Nhrefby