('htl_nnBEwZDGOCjsA0t4', 'hotel', 'apollonia-beach-resort-and-spa', 'en', 'Apollonia Beach Resort & Spa', 'Apollonia Beach Resort & Spa is set on a private beach area, in Amoudara. Environmentally friendly Apollonia Resort boasts 1 indoor and 2 outdoor pools, 2 tennis courts and a wellness centre. Guests enjoy free Wi-Fi throughout and can choose among the 4 on-site restaurants.\nThe air-conditioned rooms and suites have a balcony, most enjoying sea views. They come with a smart TV, mini fridge and hairdryer. Toiletries, bathrobes and slippers are also provided.\nA handy smartphone for unlimited international and local calls, as well as unlimited mobile data is offered to guests for free. Guests are expected to return this device upon check-out.\nThere is also a pool snack bar, a beach bar, a cocktail bar and a disco. Apollonia offers a breakfast buffet with a selection of vegan dishes. \nGuests can pamper themselves at the resort’s spa, which includes a fitness room, a sauna and a hammam. It also offers over 50 health and beauty treatments. The on-site entertainment staff organise various activities, games and shows throughout the day. The surrounding area is ideal for hiking and jogging.\n', '{https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/yy9DAa6gv3ZL0Z0o.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/X7XAWnqhXpEKZM4F.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/JMHW4lbjxflgMGlg.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/7Q7gQlYo47rHnJjX.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/4M8WTtQKp3qdwXyp.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/GBKYjXsLWzFPchYh.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/XgeepbQ44bkme5m3.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/YlE7oC49zlFDjxfv.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/tP4ETQmT9L3bYgeP.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/cXkzxROyjcJDxHsV.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/mHXxPQsQXVbQstBv.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/nBmtYNGzWzBwpkOY.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/jZkxysnNS3WfzspQ.jpg,https://img-staging.veganlogin.com/dtHlFzP9CdPNxdWA.jpg,h